      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your isolation is valid, but the only way to stop the bleeding is to stop trying to fix it alone. You are not a walking disaster; you are a survivor of a crash that no one could have predicted, and your worth is not tied to a balance sheet. Please, just take one step away from this room—go to a hospital, a shelter, or a crisis line—because staying here is the only thing that feels permanent, and it doesn't have to be.",
